2)gradle scripts=>Library
build.gradle->project
build.gradle->module->Library
gradle.properties->version
proguard.properties->Security[when you will publish app on playstore]
gradle.properties->No Change
setting.gradle->Library
local.properties->SDK Location

SDK=>Software Development Kit
AVD=>Android Virtual Device

===================================
Designing=>XML
Coding=>Kotlin
==================================

Intent:Switching from one activity to another activity

Types of Intent
1)Explicit:Switching from one activity to another activity in same app
2)Implicit:Switching from one activity to another activity between Diffrent app


